830
00:49:29,967 --> 00:49:33,347
Tell me, do you still want
to become a full demon?

831
00:49:33,471 --> 00:49:34,011
‐Yeah.

832
00:49:34,138 --> 00:49:35,138
Of course I do.

833
00:49:35,222 --> 00:49:38,102
‐You’re pretty strong
already, don’t you think?

834
00:49:38,184 --> 00:49:40,064
‐Be quiet, will ya?

835
00:49:40,144 --> 00:49:42,024
