just quit bugging me about it,

837
00:49:45,191 --> 00:49:45,731
would ya?

838
00:49:48,903 --> 00:49:50,493
‐I’ve been thinking,
there’s nothing wrong

839
00:49:50,613 --> 00:49:53,413
with staying the way you are.

840
00:49:53,491 --> 00:49:54,951
I mean, why not
stay a half demon?

841
00:49:59,747 --> 00:50:03,667
To be honest, I like you
just the way you are.

842
00:50:03,751 --> 00:50:04,751
‐That’s ridiculous.

843
00:50:04,835 --> 00:50:06,245
‐What’s so ridiculous?

844
00:50:06,337 --> 00:50:07,797
Can’t you be a little serious?

845
00:50:16,305 --> 00:50:17,935
‐What is it now?

846
00:50:18,015 --> 00:50:18,925
‐Inuyasha?

847
00:50:19,016 --> 00:50:20,056
You just‐‐

848
00:50:20,184 --> 00:50:20,934
‐Come on.

849
00:50:21,018 --> 00:50:21,688
Spit it out.

850
00:50:25,022 --> 00:50:25,522
‐Hey.

851
00:50:25,606 --> 00:50:26,356
What’s that?

852
00:50:26,440 --> 00:50:27,610
‐Strange.

853
00:50:27,691 --> 00:50:30,781
How can cherry blossoms
fall in this season?

854
00:50:30,861 --> 00:50:31,861
‐What‐‐ what’s wrong?

855
00:50:42,790 --> 00:50:44,330
KAGUYA: The time has now come.

856
00:50:44,416 --> 00:50:47,786
Behold the robe from heaven
to drape upon my shoulders.

857
00:50:47,878 --> 00:50:51,378
And for you, it is but a
deep sadness that I feel.

858
00:50:54,510 --> 00:50:57,050
‐Thanks for saving me the
trouble of hunting you down.

859
00:50:59,890 --> 00:51:01,890
‐Not the two of you again.

860
00:51:02,017 --> 00:51:06,397
What poor luck I have to
come across such fools.

861
00:51:06,522 --> 00:51:08,402
Where is the celestial robe?

862
00:51:08,524 --> 00:51:11,324
‐What are you talking about?

863
00:51:11,402 --> 00:51:13,322
‐There it is.

864
00:51:13,404 --> 00:51:15,244
‐You ain’t gettin’ it!

865
00:51:18,826 --> 00:51:21,156
[chanting]

866
00:51:24,748 --> 00:51:25,708
‐What?

867
00:51:25,791 --> 00:51:26,791
‐You won’t interfere.

868
00:51:37,094 --> 00:51:38,554
‐Inuyasha!

869
00:51:38,637 --> 00:51:40,557
‐What’s happening?

870
00:51:40,639 --> 00:51:43,269
‐I wondered why
you were so weak.

871
00:51:43,392 --> 00:51:44,482
Now I see.

872
00:51:44,602 --> 00:51:45,982
You’re merely a half demon.

873
00:51:46,103 --> 00:51:49,313
‐That a problem for ya?

874
00:51:49,440 --> 00:51:49,770
‐Inuyasha!

875
00:51:54,403 --> 00:51:54,613
‐Kagome!

876
00:51:54,737 --> 00:51:55,277
‐Inuyasha!

877
00:52:01,076 --> 00:52:01,576
‐Yes.

878
00:52:01,660 --> 00:52:02,660
There it is.

879
00:52:02,786 --> 00:52:05,746
The celestial robe for
which I’ve searched.

880
00:52:05,831 --> 00:52:08,171
[chanting]

881
00:52:08,292 --> 00:52:09,252
‐Run, you fool!

882
00:52:13,213 --> 00:52:15,763
‐Kaguya!

883
00:52:15,841 --> 00:52:18,471
‐Such impudence.

884
00:52:18,552 --> 00:52:19,802
A sacred arrow.

885
00:52:22,306 --> 00:52:23,806
Interesting.

886
00:52:23,891 --> 00:52:25,521
‐Release Inuyasha now.

887
00:52:25,643 --> 00:52:28,813
‐Get out of here, Kagome!

888
00:52:28,896 --> 00:52:31,476
‐Just go ahead and try it.

889
00:52:31,607 --> 00:52:33,727
‐It’s your funeral.

890
00:52:33,817 --> 00:52:37,817
[chanting]

891
00:52:47,831 --> 00:52:49,671
‐Inuyasha!

892
00:52:49,750 --> 00:52:51,250
‐Kagome!

893
00:52:51,335 --> 00:52:51,845
‐Watch out!

894
00:53:03,722 --> 00:53:04,102
‐Kagome.

895
00:53:07,851 --> 00:53:08,191
Kagome!

896
00:53:14,066 --> 00:53:17,936
‐I’m so thankful‐‐ you’re
all right, Inuyasha.

897
00:53:18,028 --> 00:53:19,398
‐Why did you do that?

898
00:53:19,530 --> 00:53:21,820
Why didn’t you stay away?

899
00:53:21,907 --> 00:53:23,367
‐It’s no big deal.

900
00:53:23,450 --> 00:53:28,790
And besides, you’re always
saving me, aren’t you?

901
00:53:28,872 --> 00:53:29,752
‐Kagome.

902
00:53:29,873 --> 00:53:30,753
Kagome!

903
00:53:30,874 --> 00:53:32,214
Kagome!

904
00:53:32,334 --> 00:53:33,794
Kagome!

905
00:53:33,877 --> 00:53:35,247
[laughter]

906
00:53:35,379 --> 00:53:36,419
‐Damn.

907
00:53:36,547 --> 00:53:37,757
Let me go, you creepy witch.

908
00:53:37,881 --> 00:53:42,141
If Kagome dies, you’re gonna
regret the day you ever met me.

909
00:53:42,219 --> 00:53:46,889
‐Oh, rest assured, I will
not let her die so easily.

910
00:53:46,974 --> 00:53:50,734
Now, will you become my servant?

911
00:53:50,853 --> 00:53:52,903
Do so, and I shall
grant you a wish.

912
00:53:56,442 --> 00:53:57,232
‐You go to hell.

913
00:53:57,317 --> 00:54:00,357
Release me, that’s
all I want from you.

914
00:54:00,446 --> 00:54:05,406
‐Then I’m taking the
girl along with me.

915
00:54:05,492 --> 00:54:05,872
‐No!

916
00:54:05,951 --> 00:54:06,911
Put her down!

917
00:54:06,994 --> 00:54:08,294
Where are you taking her?

918
00:54:11,248 --> 00:54:13,788
‐Come to my dream castle.

919
00:54:13,917 --> 00:54:15,247
That is, if you so desire.

920
00:54:19,256 --> 00:54:21,256
You can’t escape me for long.

921
00:54:28,265 --> 00:54:28,595
Dammit!

922
00:54:32,978 --> 00:54:35,938
Shippo, where’s this
dream castle of hers?

923
00:54:36,023 --> 00:54:37,733
‐Wh‐‐what are you asking me for?

924
00:54:37,816 --> 00:54:38,816
How should I know?

925
00:54:38,942 --> 00:54:40,362
‐Wait.

926
00:54:40,444 --> 00:54:42,824
There’s a saying a priest
once told my family.

927
00:54:42,946 --> 00:54:45,196
Perhaps it can help
us find the castle.

928
00:54:45,282 --> 00:54:48,912
The castle of the heavenly being
lies in the lake of Motosu,

929
00:54:48,994 --> 00:54:50,664
unreachable by mortals.

930
00:54:55,584 --> 00:54:58,714
‐So tell me, Hachi, why do you
think my grandfather didn’t

931
00:54:58,796 --> 00:55:01,086
use his wind tunnel
on this Kaguya?

932
00:55:01,173 --> 00:55:02,973
‐Oh, come on, isn’t it obvious?

933
00:55:03,050 --> 00:55:05,140
Your grandfather
destroy a woman?

934
00:55:05,260 --> 00:55:07,640
This celestial maiden was
probably a real beauty.

935
00:55:11,099 --> 00:55:12,979
‐You don’t say?

936
00:55:13,101 --> 00:55:15,101
I’m quite looking
forward to meeting her.

937
00:55:15,187 --> 00:55:16,397
‐You never change.

938
00:55:16,480 --> 00:55:18,230
Always on the prowl.

939
00:55:18,315 --> 00:55:19,185
[laughter]

940
00:55:26,031 --> 00:55:29,331
‐Whoa, is this the
cave of the shrine?

941
00:55:29,409 --> 00:55:29,659
‐Hush.

942
00:55:33,163 --> 00:55:34,663
Someone has arrived ahead of us.

943
00:55:43,465 --> 00:55:44,835
‐Huh?

944
00:55:44,925 --> 00:55:46,015
‐Don’t move a muscle.

945
00:55:55,060 --> 00:55:57,980
Please, hang on, Sango!

946
00:55:58,063 --> 00:55:59,983
‐Is that you, Miroku?

947
00:56:00,065 --> 00:56:02,525
What are you doing here?

948
00:56:02,609 --> 00:56:04,859
‐Sango?

949
00:56:04,945 --> 00:56:07,115
How I longed to see you!

950
00:56:07,197 --> 00:56:08,697
‐Miroku, come on.

951
00:56:08,824 --> 00:56:09,374
What are you doing?

952
00:56:14,329 --> 00:56:14,539
Stop it.

953
00:56:14,663 --> 00:56:15,873
Let go!

954
00:56:15,956 --> 00:56:17,166
Let go of me!

955
00:56:20,878 --> 00:56:22,668
‐How my hands have
yearned for this.

956
00:56:22,754 --> 00:56:25,594
[slap]

957
00:56:25,716 --> 00:56:28,086
‐Ah, this pain brings
back fond memories.

958
00:56:28,218 --> 00:56:31,008
It’s been far, far
too long, Sango.

959
00:56:31,096 --> 00:56:34,806
‐Well, you haven’t changed
a bit, you pervert.

960
00:56:34,892 --> 00:56:35,352
‐I know.

961
00:56:35,434 --> 00:56:36,024
I know.

962
00:56:41,106 --> 00:56:43,686
I’m glad you found
Kohaku safe and sound.

963
00:56:43,775 --> 00:56:44,605
‐Yes.

964
00:56:44,735 --> 00:56:48,865
Unfortunately, his
memory is still unclear.

965
00:56:48,947 --> 00:56:50,617
‐It’s gone.

966
00:56:50,741 --> 00:56:51,491
