967
00:56:51,575 --> 00:56:52,995
e mirror, as well
as the jeweled sprig.

968
00:56:53,076 --> 00:56:54,286
They’re both gone.

969
00:56:54,411 --> 00:56:56,541
‐The swallow’s cowrie
shell is gone, as well.

970
00:56:56,622 --> 00:56:59,252
Kagura came and
stole it from Kohaku.

971
00:56:59,333 --> 00:57:03,003
MIROKU: This poses
a serious problem.

972
00:57:03,086 --> 00:57:06,086
HACHI: Master Miroku, was
this cowrie thing also

973
00:57:06,173 --> 00:57:08,883
necessary to break the spell?

974
00:57:08,967 --> 00:57:09,927
‐It was.

975
00:57:10,469 --> 00:57:13,299
