represent the five elements.

976
00:57:13,430 --> 00:57:16,470
And those five elements are
wood, fire, earth, metal,

977
00:57:16,600 --> 00:57:17,730
and water.

978
00:57:17,809 --> 00:57:21,349
‐Ah‐‐ one of the five treasures
is the cost of the fire rat.

979
00:57:21,438 --> 00:57:25,108
Do you think it could be the
same cloth that Inuyasha wears?

980
00:57:25,233 --> 00:57:27,283
‐If so, we’ll meet up
with him soon enough.

981
00:57:37,204 --> 00:57:40,834
‐A castle in the lake.

982
00:57:40,958 --> 00:57:42,168
‐I can’t believe
the demonic aura.

983
00:57:46,296 --> 00:57:49,126
‐Time and the full moon are
fully aligned once more.

984
00:57:49,257 --> 00:57:52,137
An eternal dream, a
celebration this night.

985
00:57:52,260 --> 00:57:53,760
And now, let it all begin.

986
00:58:44,354 --> 00:58:46,114
‐Our fears are justified.

987
00:58:46,189 --> 00:58:49,109
‐The demonic aura
is growing stronger.

988
00:58:49,192 --> 00:58:51,742
‐She stops time without
care or remorse,

989
00:58:51,862 --> 00:58:54,862
and destroys all living
things in her wake.

990
00:58:58,785 --> 00:58:59,155
‐Huh?

991
00:59:02,247 --> 00:59:04,167
‐There’s a glow
beyond the forest.

992
00:59:04,249 --> 00:59:05,999
