993
00:59:06,084 --> 00:59:10,844
‐I don’t know about you two,
but shouldn’t we avoid danger?

994
00:59:10,922 --> 00:59:13,592
‐Well, if that’s how you feel,
then stay here out of the way,

995
00:59:13,717 --> 00:59:14,587
OK?

996
00:59:14,718 --> 00:59:16,048
‐Inuyasha!

997
00:59:16,178 --> 00:59:17,468
