now, we’ll be done for!

1000
00:59:22,017 --> 00:59:22,517
‐Good point!

1001
01:00:17,447 --> 01:00:18,317
‐Damn there, Kilala.

1002
01:00:25,330 --> 01:00:25,870
Kilala!

1003
01:00:31,253 --> 01:00:32,923
‐Master, we’d better be careful.

1004
01:00:33,004 --> 01:00:33,344
‐Oh, no.

1005
01:00:33,463 --> 01:00:36,173
Hachi, watch out!

1006
01:00:36,299 --> 01:00:36,629
‐Miroku!

1007
01:00:36,758 --> 01:00:37,678
No!

1008
01:00:37,801 --> 01:00:39,301
[scream]

1009
01:00:50,355 --> 01:00:51,435
‐Hachi, are you all right?

1010
01:00:51,523 --> 01:00:54,483
Please, speak to me.

1011
01:00:54,568 --> 01:00:54,648
Hachi!

1012
01:00:58,155 --> 01:00:59,205
Hachi!

1013
01:00:59,322 --> 01:01:03,332
[snoring]

1014
01:01:10,417 --> 01:01:13,127
‐Kohaku, I want you
to hang on tight, OK?

1015
01:01:13,211 --> 01:01:13,751
‐Yes, Miss Sango.

1016
01:01:18,175 --> 01:01:19,055
‐Look.

1017
01:01:19,176 --> 01:01:19,836
There’s something in the water.

1018
01:01:29,728 --> 01:01:31,098
‐Sango!

1019
01:01:31,188 --> 01:01:33,018
‐Shippo!

1020
01:01:33,106 --> 01:01:34,726
‐Kagome!

1021
01:01:34,858 --> 01:01:36,438
‐Inuyasha!

1022
01:01:36,526 --> 01:01:37,686
