1023
01:01:42,282 --> 01:01:42,822
INUYASHA: Kagome!

1024
01:01:42,908 --> 01:01:44,448
Are you all right?

1025
01:01:49,372 --> 01:01:56,552
‐Inu‐‐ Inuyasha?

1026
01:01:56,671 --> 01:01:58,971
Inuyasha!

1027
01:01:59,049 --> 01:02:01,719
‐The wound has healed.

1028
01:02:01,801 --> 01:02:05,221
Such is the power of
the celestial robe.

1029
01:02:05,347 --> 01:02:09,427
My wish shall be realized.

1030
01:02:09,559 --> 01:02:11,729
‐Kagome, I’m coming to save you!

1031
01:02:11,811 --> 01:02:14,901
Just hang on!
Don’t give up on me!

1032
01:02:15,023 --> 01:02:17,363
‐Inuyasha!

1033
01:02:23,031 --> 01:02:23,531
‐What the‐‐

1034
01:02:27,702 --> 01:02:28,792
[scream]

1035
01:02:31,957 --> 01:02:32,497
That’s a‐‐

1036
01:03:04,698 --> 01:03:06,868
‐I knew I shouldn’t have
come along with you.

1037
01:03:23,300 --> 01:03:23,630
‐Damn!

1038
01:03:36,271 --> 01:03:36,601
Wind Scar!

1039
01:03:48,158 --> 01:03:49,778
This is taking too long.

1040
01:03:49,868 --> 01:03:52,578
I’ll use my Backlash Wave
and destroy it with one blow.

1041
01:04:02,422 --> 01:04:03,842
