1050
01:05:04,692 --> 01:05:05,902
INUYASHA (VOICEOVER): I get it.

1051
01:05:05,985 --> 01:05:07,565
They’re all connected
at the base.

1052
01:05:07,654 --> 01:05:09,204
If I can destroy that‐‐

1053
01:05:17,455 --> 01:05:20,415
‐Watch this!

1054
01:05:20,500 --> 01:05:20,880
Wind Scar!

1055
01:05:35,598 --> 01:05:39,598
